\begin_layout Standard
Then the graph function 
\begin_inset Formula $S\longrightarrow S_{\text{\textbf{Cd}}}^{I}$
\end_inset

 that assigns each arrow in 
\begin_inset Formula $s:c\rightarrow c'$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

